_description: On the interpretation of the name ‘Ihc’ — forty-eight lines mainly in quatrains

BLEge3245.First Lines: These lettris tþre wiþ þe titilArn mochil of myht…
BLEge3245.Last Lines: …We prey þe for sinne dampne vs nouhtbut our socour & saueour þu be
